<br>
As far as I am concerned, we are talking about the same issue - Sev re: warrior the epic V the other epics.  <br>
<br>
I have been playing this game for 3 years and I worked like hell to get my epic.  Yes, I did it in one month ... but in that one month .. I turned down all sorts to get there.  I normally abide by rules that I dont let EQ take away my normal sleeping pattern, but was up in PoA until 10am in the morning, killed Talendor, cleared Chardok, got a friend to MQ the PoF piece, went to PoH and waited my turn -  I basically used the network of friends to help me as I has helped them before.  I put the time in, I got the reward.  Same with Sev, I didnt camp him so I didnt get lucky, but I had a friend camping him whilst I was camping the old ragefire for my friend(which I had to camp for 3 separate people - only once was I lucky)<br>
<br>
I despise doing quests of any kind and Warrior epic was no exception.  <br>
<br>
Although Sev is quite a long camp granted, the reward is there to be had.  <br>
<br>
The warrior epic imho is no where near one of the hardest epics.  On the rare occasion, Verant has made us an exception and given us definitely not the easiest epic (monk/shaman/druid) but definitelty not the hardest (paladin/SK/mage or necro - cant remember which?) .  Again I dont know enough bout the stages of their epics to comment on them. More of a case of the nightmare parts.<br>
<br>
The is no other replacement for the cleric epic, that means EVERY cleric wants and needs it, same goes for the other classes in a lot of cases.  <br>
<br>
For the warriors, this is different kettle of fish. There are so many weapons just as easy to access that are compariable or better than the warrior epic.  I have had a Silver sword of yelnak cross my hands not long back thats 13/24 - thats not bad, Willsapper 13/20? or 12/20 or something + slow = a great weapon - Vaniki is not tough at all.  Prolly easier than Sev, I came across a mob that drops a 15/20 weapon in Griegs end.  Never fought him before but he dont seem that hard tbh.  Frostbringer aint far behind the epic.  There are loads of weapons better than the main hand epic, and plenty to replace the offhand.  <br>
<br>
The warrior epic is awkward, and yes a bottleneck has occurred with Sev ... but I dont find people camping Sev on our server.  ever.  Everytime I have passed through EJ, Sev hasnt been camped.  <br>
<br>
Ragefire is always camped without exception.<br>
<br>
This (from Quellious experience) has made Ragefire more of a target for KSing than Sev.  Sev has never been KSed on our server - we would have heard about it.<br>
<br>
